Tumble - Series 1, Episode 6




Show Six

The remaining (6) celebrities will perform two disciplines each. The first discipline is a combined floor and aerial trapeze performance. Celebrities will receive comments and scores from the judges. After this, viewer voting opens. The judges' scoring is for guidance only, as it is viewer votes alone which will decide who is crowned Tumble Champion 2014. The celebrities will then perform their second discipline, the vault. This will not be scored. Viewer voting will close as announced in the programme and the winner will be revealed at the end of the show.




Original Air Date: 13-Sep-2014
